Ref: LocationConfiguration.Location > Locations.id
Ref: LocationConfiguration.ItemType > LocationConfigurationItemTypes.id
Ref: WarehouseEquipmentSerial.Equipment > Equipment.id
Ref: WarehouseEquipmentSerial.Warehouse > Warehouses.id
Ref: SubCorrectiveEvent.CorrectiveEvent > CorrectiveEvents.id
